FBIS3-12236 "drnes028_m_94021" FBIS-NES-94-028 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 JORDAN Husayn Calls al-Hirawi, Denounces Church Incident JN2702162194 Amman Jordan Television Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 27 Feb 94 JN2702162194 Amman Jordan Television Network Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] In a telephone conversation with His Excellency Lebanese President Ilyas al-Hirawi today, His Majesty King Husayn denounced the criminal incident that occurred in Sayyidat al-Najat church in Lebanon this morning, killing innocent worshipers. On behalf of himself and the people and Government of Jordan, his majesty offered to his excellency the Lebanese president his sincerest condolences for the victims of the outrageous incident.
